creator: Ugolkov Sergey
descriptionHtml: Calculating the cost of a product has never been so easy. Now for this you do not need a pen, sheets and a calculator or even an Excel spreadsheet. You can do it directly on your phone or tablet and for this you just need to add the necessary components, indicating their cost, and create a product by adding the necessary components to it. The application will help to calculate the cost, not only to the cook and pastry chef, but also to those who are engaged in needlework or construction.
descriptionShort: The Prime Cost application will help you calculate the cost of your products.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Added the ability to sort products and components by name.
Improved application stability.

title: Prime Cost

container.value: 125430, г. Москва, пер. Митинский 2-й, д.5, кв. 324

creator: Ugolkov Sergey
descriptionHtml:
Prime Cost - It's easy

The application will help you easily and simply calculate the cost of the product. It doesn't matter who you are - a confectioner, perfumer, carpenter or seamstress, the application will help you calculate the cost of an apple pie, soap, perfume or any other product, be it wood, fabric or any other material.

The application separates concepts such as products and components. Components are part of a product. This allows you to reuse the same components in different products, which saves you from the routine of writing the same components for you in different products.

The cost calculation is carried out on the basis of the components used in the product. But if you want to take into account your labor costs or other expenses in the cost price, then you can add them to the added value field. You can also include taxes in the calculation of the cost of the product. You just need to enter the tax rate in the VAT field when creating the item.

To improve the recognition of a product, component or catalog, a photo and description can be added to each of them.

The distribution of products and components by catalogs will allow you not to get confused in them and put everything on the shelves.

It will be possible to make calculations for a different number of products without using a calculator, but simply by adding a calculation for a certain number of products.

In the application, you can add not only products and components, but also units of measure for them.

Local and cloud backup will not lose your data if you change your phone.
descriptionShort: The Prime Cost application will help you calculate the cost of your products.

appDetails.developerAddress: 125430, Россия, г. Москва, пер. Митинский 2-й, д.5, кв. 324
appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Work has been done to improve the stability of the application.

I hope I managed to make the application a little bit more better)

title: Prime Cost

container.value: 125430, Россия, г. Москва, пер. Митинский 2-й, д.5, кв. 324

creator: Ugolkov Sergey
descriptionHtml:
Prime Cost - It's easy

The application will help you easily and simply calculate the cost of the product. It doesn't matter who you are - a confectioner, perfumer, carpenter or seamstress, the application will help you calculate the cost of an apple pie, soap, perfume or any other product, be it wood, fabric or any other material.

The application separates concepts such as products and components. Components are part of a product. This allows you to reuse the same components in different products, which saves you from the routine of writing the same components for you in different products.

The cost calculation is carried out on the basis of the components used in the product. But if you want to take into account your labor costs or other expenses in the cost price, then you can add them to the added value field. You can also include taxes in the calculation of the cost of the product. You just need to enter the tax rate in the VAT field when creating the item.

To improve the recognition of a product, component or catalog, a photo and description can be added to each of them.

The distribution of products and components by catalogs will allow you not to get confused in them and put everything on the shelves.

It will be possible to make calculations for a different number of products without using a calculator, but simply by adding a calculation for a certain number of products.

In the application, you can add not only products and components, but also units of measure for them.

Local and cloud backup will not lose your data if you change your phone.
